      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm trying to plan a trip from Heathrow to Edinburgh and i'm a bit worried about missing connections. if i take the heathrow express to paddington then catch an LNER train up north, what's a safe amount of time to leave between those two? also i'll need to catch a local bus once i get to edinburgh so i want to make sure the whole itinerary is solid. thanks.",
      "source": "evaluator"
